## Write-Only Client Secret

Prefer `client_secret_wo` with `client_secret_wo_version` for secret rotation without persisting the supplied client secret value in Terraform state.

{{ .SchemaMarkdown | trimspace }}

## Import

OIDC identity provider configurations can be imported using the configuration name:

```shell
# Import the default configuration
terraform import minio_iam_idp_openid.default _

# Import a named configuration
terraform import minio_iam_idp_openid.keycloak keycloak
```

Note: `client_secret` is not returned by the MinIO API and must be set in your configuration after import.
